'''Greg Titus''' is an illustrator and concept artist. He penciled the comic "[[All for You]]," a part of ''[[Star Wars Tales 17]]''. While working at Pilot Studio from 2014 to 2019, he developed the art and was the principal illustrator for [[Star Wars: The Black Series|the Black Series]] of action figures.<ref name="Gregory Titus">{{WebCite|url=https://www.gregorytitus.com/about |text=Gregory Titus Illustration: About|archivedate=20240111054502
}}</ref> Titus has done artwork for other comic books, products and brands. He lives in Massachusetts.

